  "text": "PyCon Namibia is back for 2024! 🇳🇦 4th-7th March.\n\nEach 500 CZK donated to the conference allows us to provide another free ticket to someone who would not otherwise be able to attend. There is a special \"Supporter donation\" ticket on https://lnkd.in/edsEW6Sf, where you can specify exactly how much you want to send. Each 500 CZK pays for one disadvantaged pythonista! 💸\n\nWhat did we already achieve?\n\n👉 5 people donated last year, see special post made to celebrate Czech contributions 🇨🇿 https://lnkd.in/e65kGfQV\n\n👉 2 people from Czechia are actually coming to visit this year's PyCon Namibia! 🤠 Cheers to Mia Bajić and Karolina Surma 👏\n\n👉 Domitil Katemo gave a talk about Python community in Namibia at PyCon CZ last year! See https://lnkd.in/enQYxnX9, hopefully soon with a video recording.\n\n👉 Patreon page up to ~1,200 CZK/mo so far https://lnkd.in/eEXiWZzM\n\n👉 Interview with Jessica Upani I made a while back is still getting some traction, ~250 people read the article so far https://lnkd.in/eZt_PeK\n\nI'm happy to see progress. We've seen people donating to the cause, now we see people actually flying to Namibia and attending the conference ❤️ It seems like these statuses I post every year have some impact after all!\n\nI already bought my donation, now it's your turn 😉 Let's make the list of names on the \"thank you\" poster longer then last year! We can do it!",
